property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"And the blue team won again!"},{"frame":10,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Wh... why we lost? We had true friendship by our side!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Friendship? What do you mean?"},{"frame":11,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"The 'tech' you stolen from our fort is... just the way we respect each other..."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"You... red Nerd... aren't you... dominating the other units?! Are you friends?!"},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Exactly. Sometime we go dancing, play RPGs and excercise together. We meet at the bar every morning."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"It's... impossible. Girls don't like nerds... Nerds don't like Machos... and..."},{"frame":5,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Mr. General. 'Red Nerd' is my boyfriend."},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Oh. That's... too much. How... you managed to..."},{"frame":3,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Hey, glass guy. That's nothing new. We ARE friends. We love your water battles..."},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"..."},{"frame":6,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"...because we've a lot of fun! We are happy when we're with you!"},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"It's... not... for my military skills..."},{"frame":5,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Aw, come on! Your military skills are pretty amazing! But it's just one part of you!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Aw. I. I got it. You, guys..."},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Yes! They are battling with you because they are your friends, not your units!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"... So. I have... different friends. Now. It's... it's..."},{"frame":9,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Aw, General. Come on. Let's go all together to the bar for a beer!"},{"frame":9,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Outstanding idea, Blue Bro! We've to celebrate the end of the Royal Water Battles!"},{"frame":8,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Let's march to the bar! One-two-three-four! One-two-three-four!"},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Right! Well, as the General... I propose here and now an eternal peace treaty between Red and Blue!"},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Red Team agrees! And we need a cool name for this. Something that will be remembered!"},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"I've that too. The 'Water Seal' will bond us all together for this summer and forever!"},{"frame":7,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"AWWW YEEEAH!"},{"frame":9,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"AND THE GENERAL WILL OFFER FOR US ALL!"},{"frame":8,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"LET'S GO!"},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"H-HEY! IT'S NOT FAIR! HEY GUYS... COME BACK!"},{"frame":0,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"'Stop!' 'Catch me, soldier!' 'Take this!' *SPLASH* 'Hey! The war is over, General!' 'It's... training!'"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"..."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Kh. Kh. Kh. Kh. Kh."},{"frame":7,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Now that the General and its team is with us, we will bring down the world..."},{"frame":0,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"...under the sacred 'Water Seal'. The war will never end, my beloved friends."}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":7,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Finally! Nerd, Girl and Macho units working together with top-notch technologies, for the Blue Team!"},{"frame":10,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"GENERAL! We've a HUGE problem..."},{"frame":7,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Be quiet, Colonel. We both have strength and technology now! Nothing is a problem!"},{"frame":12,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Hey, glasses guy. Your minion is pretty right. That guys are..."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Okay, okay. Tell me, what's this problem?"},{"frame":9,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Hey, megalomaniac! We've a pretty surprise for you!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Huh?"},{"frame":8,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"You attacked from our fort for something you could ask gently. Now you've to face the consequences."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"We just won the war, losers. Face it."},{"frame":7,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Today is the August 15th. And you know what it means?"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"The... day of the Royal Water Battles!"},{"frame":7,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Bingo! And we've surrounded and outnumbered you, this time! We are going to exterminate your team!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"... Damn."},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"General. Let's do it."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Colonel... Do it. You deserve to do it by yourself."},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"General. Thank you. Well..."},{"frame":7,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"CHAAAAARGEEEE!"},{"frame":8,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"YEEEEEAAH!"}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Everything is ready, General."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Very well, Colonel. We crossed the whole beach for reaching this battlefield. We can't lose."},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"A question, General. Why we aren't deploying the Macho units we acquired before for this mission?"},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"This is an infiltration mission, Colonel. We're the only with the crucial expertise for succeed."},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"And why we're attacking these guys? We even don't know who they are."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Colonel. Just look at them."},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Hey, you!"},{"frame":12,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Y... yes, sir!"},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Good job with the water bombs. We've plenty of them. The fort is safe."},{"frame":6,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Thank you, sir!"},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Are the gates safe, Girls?"},{"frame":5,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Yes. We're guarding them, now."},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Very well. I'll check the last things. Good job everyone."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"See? Girl, Nerd and Macho units working together. We've to understand how they made it."},{"frame":10,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"They... are so strong! I hope our special infiltration forces will come back safe and sound..."},{"frame":7,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Safe is not enough, Colonel. They've to come back victorious!"}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":11,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Hey guys... What's up?"},{"frame":3,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"What happend? You forgot your beach towel?"},{"frame":11,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Awww... no. I was talking about MMORPGs with a friend when a bunch of girls attacked us."},{"frame":3,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"But, why? They wanted to steal our strategy for this evening LAN party?"},{"frame":6,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Are these are the losers you beat this morning, girls?"},{"frame":5,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Yeah. It looks like these stupid girls have normal friends too."},{"frame":2,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Hey! Our gamer friends ARE normal too, animal!"},{"frame":5,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"See? Something is clearly wrong."},{"frame":6,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"This is Blasphemy! This is Madness!"},{"frame":9,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Madness? This is Sparta!"}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":0,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Meanwhile, not so far..."},{"frame":5,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"So that guy I've met at the bar offered me something to drink..."},{"frame":5,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"...Aaaaand? <3"},{"frame":2,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"...he told me... Wait... Is that real?"},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"The trick is to get all the potions from the shop before going there..."},{"frame":5,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"...so I can get more damage without dying. Got it."},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"...just remember to right click with the mouse to use the healing potion, ok?"},{"frame":2,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"...I... can't... believe."},{"frame":8,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"I can't stand it. Hurry. To the water guns."},{"frame":2,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Hey! Are... you okay?!"}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":10,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"General! That... that... tyrants... are coming here!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Let... them go. We can't do anything more than some water splashes. We must accept defeat."},{"frame":3,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Hey, glasses guy."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"...oh, right. I've to leave them before you punch me. Colonel, can you keep these for me?"},{"frame":6,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"You're pretty good with these buckets and guns!"},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"What...?"},{"frame":6,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"I want to join your team. Let's mess up this beach!"},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Ok, then! Ready?"},{"frame":3,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"H... hey! I'm blue now! W... what the heck...?"},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"We're the blue team! We're stronger than ever! Nobody can stop us NOW!"},{"frame":9,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Hey! Looks that some of our macho team members became nerd-lovers! Going to play the game-of-role thing? Ahahah!"},{"frame":7,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Time to fight back once for all, soldiers! Ready?"},{"frame":9,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Now that's a worthy fight! To the bucket, guys!"}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Good news and bad news, General."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Good news first, Colonel."},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"We stolen the water gun technology from the girls. We can strike ranged attacks now!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Very good. Now we can plan better strategies."},{"frame":2,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Now... The bad news, sweetie."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"You. Again. We conquered you and your people in battle. What do you want now?"},{"frame":5,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"We got a 'new technology' too, nerdy boy. And, telling the truth, it's an handsome one..."},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Oh... no..."},{"frame":8,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"I present you... THE MACHO UNIT!"},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"We... we're screwed..."},{"frame":6,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"So... are these the roaches that are bugging you girls?"},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Colonel... fill... all the buckets... call all the soldiers..."},{"frame":9,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"I'm pretty skilled on nerd beating. You won't run far."}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":10,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Bad news, General!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Calm down, Colonel. What's happening?"},{"frame":10,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Our attack to the girls didn't pass unnoticed. They are grouping on the beach and equipping for the battle!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"That's unexpected. They think battling it's too childish for them. Colonel, are you sure your informations are --"},{"frame":2,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Your loser Colonel is right, mr. General."},{"frame":10,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Wh... What? It's... impossible! She... is talking to us?"},{"frame":2,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"You didn't expect backfire, right? Aw, nerds. You think like superheroes way too much."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"I see. Well. This is war, then."},{"frame":5,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Prepare to eat dirt, mr. General. We will end this stupid war once for all."}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"We won, General! Some of the card nerds have been recruited!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"We were just preparing for the true war, Colonel. Just, look over there."},{"frame":2,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"...and then that loser asked me out."},{"frame":2,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Aw. These nerds. They're so annoying!"},{"frame":2,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"I asked him a mojito and he said that is missing that Pokemon."},{"frame":2,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"Oh. My. God."},{"frame":10,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"..."},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Colonel."},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Understood. Filling the buckets."}]

property.name: dialogue
property.value: [{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"...and then I decked myself again. Another match lost. *Sigh*"},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Rick. Your deck was mostly fillers. You'll never win a match this way!"},{"frame":1,"side":"right","team":1,"text":"I... I've been just unlucky. I've been mana flooded from the start and..."},{"frame":4,"side":"left","team":1,"text":"Yeah. The mana flood excuse. Again."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Agh. Card game nerds. The worst of the species..."},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"W... why, General? They are nerds too..."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"It's summer, Colonel. And we are on the beach. And beach is for arcade games. Not card games!"},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"R... right..."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Cards are weak, made of paper. And paper hate water. You know what I mean."},{"frame":1,"side":"left","team":0,"text":"Roger that. I'm going to fill the buckets."},{"frame":4,"side":"right","team":0,"text":"Well done, Colonel. Time to teach these losers that real games have a TV screen!"}]
